name: Saturday Night In The Afterlife
description:
An Orgy of Light v1

Souls viewed only as red, yellow and blue primary colors.
Apart from the chromatic aberration as a side effect from peering into this other dimension any secondary colors are the results of souls merging.

2560x1440 | 60fps | High@L5.2 | 2996kb/s max bit-rate | YUV 4:2:0 | 8bit
